                    <h1>Japan’s Me Too Movement and ‘Comfort Women’ Issue: Part 2 – Intersection of History and the Translation of Culture</h1>
                    <div class="writers">
                      <p><b>Posts</b>
                                              <b>Kyung-hee Cho</b><em>Assistant Professor, Institute for East Asian Studies, Sungkonghoe University</em>
                                            </p>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="metas">
                      <li><b>Created at</b><span>2019.12.24</span></li>
